text.tspan: “Please imagine a ladder, with steps numbered from 0 at the bottom to 10 at the top. The top of the ladder
represents the best possible life for you and the bottom of the ladder represents the worst possible life for you. On
which step of the ladder would you say you personally feel you stand at this time?”
Source: World Happiness Report (2022), Gapminder (v6), HYDE (v3.2), UN (2019)
Note: The value shown in a given year is the average of that year, the previous year and the following year.
